===Etymology 1===
From {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|spadu|lang=ang}}, {{term|spada|lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}}. Cognate with [[Old Frisian]] {{term|spada|lang=ofs}}, [[Old Saxon]] {{term|spado|lang=osx}}, German {{term|Spaten|lang=de}}. Ultimately from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{term/t|ine-pro|*sph₂-dʰ-}}, whence also Ancient Greek {{term|σπάθη||blade|tr=spathē|lang=grc}}, Hittite {{term||išpatar|spear}} {{rfscript|und|sc=Xsux}}.

